                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Chinese Minister</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-08-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 29, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Loomis informs Sir Chentung Liang-Cheng that the American China Development
                    Company has definitely accepted the offer of the Chinese Government, and that
                    the Government of the United States will not interpose any obstacles.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
